nist.model

Class Entry

  • java.lang.Object
    • nist.model.Entry

  • public class Entry
extends Object
    Represents an Entry for a vulnerability in the NIST data feed. Each entry contains detailed information about a specific vulnerability, including its severity, impact, exploitability, and affected software.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Carlos
